hard work with a Kingdom Hall that brings so much praise to his name, and it's all because

00:04:36.319 --> 00:04:42.870
these ones made themselves available for so long.

00:04:42.870 --> 00:04:48.670
It has taught me that Jehovah is a hero prayer, and if he hears someone praying for help,

00:04:48.670 --> 00:04:52.550
he will sense someone even if you live far away.

00:04:52.550 --> 00:04:57.470
Well Jesus told us that this message would reach all parts of the earth.

00:04:57.470 --> 00:05:02.470
This tells us that Jehovah loves all people, and when the time was right, Jehovah ensured

